                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.672/537: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The High Commissioner in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bristol</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Constantinople</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-01-13T12:00:00+02:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 13, 1927—noon</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received January 13—10:17 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>5. From sources unknown to us, Turkish press is inspired with idea that
                    ratification of the treaty by the Senate is foregone conclusion.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bristol</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
